text: Morning! Is this the Dunkin drive-thru assistant?
translation: Morning! Is this the Dunkin drive-thru assistant?

text: Absolutely! I'm your Dunkin Voice Crew member. Ready for your first sip?
translation: Absolutely! I'm your Dunkin Voice Crew member. Ready for your first sip?

text: Sí, necesito dos Caramel Craze lattes medianos y quiero saber si tienen cold foam de vainilla.
translation: Yes, I need two medium Caramel Craze lattes and I want to know if you have vanilla cold foam.

text: Claro, tenemos cold foam de vainilla. ¿Desea agregarlo a ambos lattes?
translation: Of course, we have vanilla cold foam. Would you like it on both lattes?

text: Got it—first latte capped with vanilla cold foam. Want to pair them with a bakery item?
translation: Got it—first latte capped with vanilla cold foam. Want to pair them with a bakery item?

text: 我看到有波士頓奶油甜甜圈，請加兩個，謝謝。
translation: I saw the Boston Kreme donut, please add two, thanks.

text: 已經為您添加兩個波士頓奶油甜甜圈，還需要點什麼早餐嗎？
translation: Two Boston Kreme donuts added. Would you like any breakfast sandwiches?

text: Could you tell me the protein in the Power Breakfast sandwich?
translation: Could you tell me the protein in the Power Breakfast sandwich?

text: It packs turkey sausage plus egg whites for 24g of protein. Want me to add one?
translation: It packs turkey sausage plus egg whites for 24g of protein. Want me to add one?

text: Yes, add one more and make it a combo with a large cold brew.
translation: Yes, add one more and make it a combo with a large cold brew.

text: Combo locked: Power Breakfast Sandwich and large Original Cold Brew. Anything to sweeten the drinks?
translation: Combo locked: Power Breakfast Sandwich and large Original Cold Brew. Anything to sweeten the drinks?

text: Ajoutez un shot supplémentaire d'espresso dans le cold brew, s'il vous plaît.
translation: Add an extra espresso shot in the cold brew, please.

text: Parfait, un shot supplémentaire ajouté. Voulez-vous le récapitulatif de la commande?
translation: Perfect, an extra shot has been added. Would you like the order summary?

text: You have 2 Caramel Craze Lattes (one with cold foam), 2 Boston Kreme donuts, 1 Power Breakfast Sandwich, and 1 large Cold Brew with an extra shot. Your total is $36.82 with tax.
translation: You have 2 Caramel Craze Lattes (one with cold foam), 2 Boston Kreme donuts, 1 Power Breakfast Sandwich, and 1 large Cold Brew with an extra shot. Your total is $36.82 with tax.

text: Thanks for rolling with Dunkin today! Swing to the next window and we'll have your Inspire Brands order ready.
translation: Thanks for rolling with Dunkin today! Swing to the next window and we'll have your Inspire Brands order ready.
